lead_paragraph: Chris Sale won again, pitching eight sharp innings and leading the Chicago White Sox over the Toronto Blue Jays 10-1 Tuesday night for their fifth straight win.

headline.print_headline: Sale Up to 5-0, White Sox Rout Blue Jays for 5th Win in Row
